Package com.attivio.sdk.transport

Enum DataGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DataGroup>
      • com.attivio.sdk.transport.DataGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DataGroup>
    public enum DataGroup
extends java.lang.Enum<DataGroup>
    DataGroup defines data groups of platform messages that flow through transports. Use forAuthority(String) to parse the authority into a recognized data group.
